name: Between the lines
body:
### Who we are [en]
We are an anti-capitalist and antifascist collective. We support LGBTQ movements, feminist movements, death to the imperialists and freedom to the people.

### Quem somos [pt-BR]
Somos um coletivo anti-capitalista e antifascista. Apoiamos movimentos LGBTQ, movimentos feministas, morte aos imperialistas e liberdade para o povo.

### Projects [en]
[A privacy and security wiki for protesters and collectives](https://github.com/betweenthelines/privacidade-negada/wiki). *Currently in Portuguese only*.

### Projetos [pt-BR]
[Uma wiki de privacidade e segurança para manifestantes e coletivos](https://github.com/betweenthelines/privacidade-negada/wiki).

### Support or Contact [en]
You can contact us through our [public channel](https://gitter.im/betweenthelines/betweenthelines).  
Follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/bwntl)!

### Contato ou Apoio [pt-BR]
Você pode entrar em contato com a gente pelo nosso [canal público](https://gitter.im/betweenthelines/betweenthelines).
Siga a gente no [Twitter](https://twitter.com/bwntl)!
